reviewText: The story is okay but the movie only lasted 24 minutes!  My fault for not reading all the description I guess.  Just can't bring myself to recommend this movie.  I wanted to add a new movie to my holiday collection for the grandkids to watch but was sorely disappointed and so were they.
This DVD is a riot! Smuckey the monkey is histerical and the animation is amazing! The characters are one-of-a-kind,  and the songs are pepppy! I love this DVD.
